data.title: Details of Core Companies
data.meta_description: Details of Core Companies - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information on various companies that manufacture and supply motors, generators, lighting equipment and transformers in India. It lists the name, products and website URLs of 15 companies related to motors and generators, followed by 17 companies related to lighting, and 1 company related to transformers. The companies represent manufacturers and suppliers of a range of electrical equipment including pumps, motors, lighting fixtures, transformers and related products.
